---
// Timeline.astro
---

<div class="timeline-container">
  <h3 class="timeline-title"><span class="marker-highlight">Consensus</span>: Engagement Strategy</h3>

  <div class="tl-wrap">

    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-node accent"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-1 skew-left interactive-hover">
        <div class="phase accent">Phase 1</div>
        <span class="time-label accent">1–4 months</span>
        <h4>Listening Sessions</h4>
        <p>Gathering feedback from Gowanus residents and local studio artists on traffic and congestion.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-gap gap-1"></div>

    <div class="tl-item right">
      <div class="tl-node dark"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-2 skew-right interactive-hover">
        <div class="phase dark">Phase 2</div>
        <span class="time-label dark">4–9 months</span>
        <h4>Design and Iteration</h4>
        <p>Collaborative workshops with local studios and community leaders to outline the 'Art Spine' route, balancing safety and aesthetics.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-gap gap-2"></div>

    <div class="tl-item">
      <div class="tl-node accent"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-1 skew-left interactive-hover">
        <div class="phase accent">Phase 3</div>
        <span class="time-label accent">9–12 months</span>
        <h4>Pilot Program</h4>
        <p>Expansion of the current Open Studios event (usually in October). Expansion of other similiar Arts Gowanus events. Document and iterate. </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-gap gap-3"></div>

    <div class="tl-item right">
      <div class="tl-node dark"></div>
      <div class="tl-card sharp-border uneven-clip-2 skew-right interactive-hover">
        <div class="phase dark">Phase 4</div>
        <span class="time-label dark">Year 2 and beyond</span>
        <h4>Implementation</h4>
        <p>Permanent zoning adjustments and streetscaping for the full Gowanus Art Spine.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .timeline-container {
    margin: 4rem 0;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* Wrapper: spine is a left border on this element */
  .tl-wrap {
    border-left: 4px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-dark) 20%, transparent);
    margin-left: 3rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Gap divs create coloured spine segments between cards */
  .tl-gap {
    border-left: 6px solid transparent;
    margin-left: -5px; /* overlap the wrap border */
    position: relative;
  }

  .gap-1 {
    height: 60px;
    
  }

  .gap-2 {
    height: 75px;
    
  }

  .gap-3 {
    height: 180px;
    
  }

  /* Each row */
  .tl-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Right-side cards shift over */
  .tl-item.right {
    padding-left: 45%;
  }

  /* ── NODE ── */
  .tl-node {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: -23px;  /* was -12px, now centers on the 4px border */
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tl-node.accent {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px #fff, 0 0 0 7px var(--color-accent);
  }

  .tl-node.dark {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px #fff, 0 0 0 7px var(--color-dark);
    margin-left: -23px;
  }

  /* ── CARD ── */
  .tl-card {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  /* ── LABELS ── */
  .phase {
    display: inline-block;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .phase.accent { background: var(--color-accent); }
  .phase.dark   { background: var(--color-dark); }

  .time-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .time-label.accent { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .time-label.dark   { color: var(--color-dark); }

  .tl-card h4 { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .tl-card p  { margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tl-item.right {
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>